cu.explanation_en: Changed nr_cellid from 1 to 0, which is out of range for valid NR cell IDs (must be between 1-1007), causing cell identification failure and preventing UE cell selection.

du.explanation_en: Changed nr_cellid from 1 to 0, which is out of range for valid NR cell IDs (must be between 1-1007), causing cell identification failure and preventing UE cell selection.
du.explanation_zh: 将nr_cellid从1更改为0，这超出了有效NR小区ID的范围（必须在1-1007之间），导致小区识别失败，从而阻止UE小区选择。
